OL,3,CFamily's 'grief and anger over the
OL,4,Clies' as infected blood report is
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FA woman widowed when her husband died
OL,8,Fafter being given infected blood says
OL,9,Fshe finally feels "heard" but
OL,10,F"overwhelmed" as the report into the
OL,11,Fscandal is released.
OL,13,FRay Walmsley, from Liverpool, died at
OL,14,Fthe age of 53 after contracting
OL,15,FHepatitis C from a blood transfusion
OL,17,FHis wife Louise Walmsley and sister
OL,18,FKaren Deasy spoke about their relief
OL,19,Fat finally being heard.
