OL,7,FLouise said: "We feel grief for Ray,
OL,8,Fwe feel anger over the cover-up and
OL,9,Fthe lies that have been told for
OL,10,Fdecades and decades, we feel relief
OL,11,Fbecause Sir Brian has heard us and he
OL,12,Fdetails in the report the horrendous
OL,13,Fway Ray and others were treated."
OL,15,FThe long-awaited report released on
OL,16,FMonday revealed the risks were "well-
OL,17,Fknown" decades before the infected
OL,18,Fblood products were used on patients
OL,19,Fin the UK.
