OL,7,FLabelled the "worst treatment disaster
OL,8,Fin the NHS", the saw more than 30,000
OL,9,Fpeople infected with HIV and Hepatitis
OL,10,FC after being treated with
OL,11,Fcontaminated blood products.
OL,13,FNicola Leahey from Chorley is a
OL,14,Fsurvivor of the scandal who has also
OL,15,Fwelcomed the final report, saying "at
OL,16,Flong last we have seen the failures in
OL,17,Fblack and white".
