OL,4,Clies' as infected blood report is
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FNicola contracted Hepatitis C from an
OL,8,Finfected blood transfusion in the
OL,9,F1980s, but she was not properly
OL,10,Fdiagnosed until 2009.
OL,12,FNicola said: "I had flu like symptoms
OL,13,Fand the Doctors blamed it on that I
OL,14,Fhad a young family and three children
OL,15,Funder five, I was struck off one of
OL,16,Fthe doctors lists for being a
OL,17,Fhypochondriac.
OL,19,F"Finally I got another GP and demanded
OL,20,Fmore blood tests and found out I had
OL,21,FHepatitis C."
