OL,7,FNicola was one of the many campaigners
OL,8,Fin London to hear the results of the
OL,9,Freport. "At long last we have got to
OL,10,Fthe end of this," she said.
OL,12,F"It is a very good, evidence based
OL,13,Fdetailed report, everything has come
OL,14,Fout that we have listened to in the
OL,15,Finquiry, the cover up and not
OL,16,Faccepting the truth and we've seen it
OL,17,Fin black and white now, the failures."
