OL,7,FIt is expected the government will lay
OL,8,Fout their plans on how they will
OL,9,Fcompensate victims on Tuesday in
OL,10,FParliament.
OL,12,FThe cost of compensation is expected
OL,13,Fto be around #10 billion.
OL,15,FNicola said: "It isn't all about money
OL,16,Fbut it is compensation for everybody,
OL,17,Fafter the wait it is something that we
OL,18,Fdeserve."
