OL,4,Clies' as infected blood report is
OL,5,Creleased
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister Rishi Sunak is
OL,8,Fexpected to issue an apology following
OL,9,Fthe publication of the report on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FA Government spokesman said: "This was
OL,13,Fan appalling tragedy that never should
OL,14,Fhave happened.
OL,16,F"We are clear that justice needs to be
OL,17,Fdone and swiftly, which is why have
OL,18,Facted in amending the Victims and
OL,19,FPrisoners Bill."
