OL,7,F"This includes establishing a new body
OL,8,Fto deliver an Infected Blood
OL,9,FCompensation Scheme, confirming the
OL,10,FGovernment will make the required
OL,11,Fregulations for it within three months
OL,12,Fof Royal Assent, and that it will have
OL,13,Fall the funding needed to deliver
OL,14,Fcompensation once they have identified
OL,15,Fthe victims and assessed claims."
OL,17,F"In addition, we have included a
OL,18,Fstatutory duty to provide additional
OL,19,Finterim payments to the estates of
OL,20,Fdeceased infected people."
